E-souq is a full stack web application that serves as an online marketplace selling electronic products.
The platform allows users to list, browse, and purchase electronic items.
E-souq delivers a functional & modern shopping experience.



# Backend Implementation:
JAVA 17 - Language Used
Spring Boot v3 - Application Structure
Spring Data JPA - Database Persistence
Spring MVC - REST API controller integration
MariaDB - Relational database implementation
Maven - Dependency management

# Frontend Implementation:
HTML5 - Page structure
CSS + SemanticUI - Page styling and responsiveness
JavaScript - Dynamic buttons & views
Fetch API - REST API consumption